The paper deals with the deployment of autonomous drones to improve user experience in cellular networks, which falls under the category of networked systems (cs.NI) and robotics (cs.RO). The paper also involves optimization techniques and algorithms (cs.IT), as well as system modeling and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes the use of machine learning techniques to build a UE density function (cs.AI).
